&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an AR Credit &amp;amp; Collections Specialist to support collection activities and credit review processes associated with our Order-to-Cash. This role works closely with customers, Account Executives, Customer Success Managers, and the Billing team to drive timely payment resolution, assess credit risk, and minimize financial exposure while maintaining positive customer relationships.&amp;nbsp;This is a hybrid role and is open to applicants located within Mexico City, Mexico. In this role, you will report to the Senior Manager, Accounting Operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
