&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Workflow &amp;amp; Configuration Design: &lt;/strong&gt;Design and optimize complex workflows, custom fields, and automation rules across all functions the PMO supports. Align configuration with PMO governance standards and program methodology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Integration &amp;amp; Add-on Management: &lt;/strong&gt;Partner with IT to manage and evaluate Atlassian add-ons and integrations with other enterprise systems (e.g. identity management, CI/CD pipelines, business intelligence tools).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Governance &amp;amp; Compliance: &lt;/strong&gt;Collaborate with PMO leadership to enforce governance standards and audit/document existing processes. Maintain documentation of system configurations and help ensure data integrity and effective platform utilization. Appropriately escalate potential risks or concerns when needed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tooling Strategy &amp;amp; Adoption: &lt;/strong&gt;Implement tools — including AI-powered solutions — against operational needs and drive enterprise rollout. Develop user documentation and training that enables self-service across all business functions.&lt;/li&gt;
