&lt;li&gt;3 to 5 years of proven experience as an Atlassian Administrator in an enterprise environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least one Atlassian certification preferred: Certified Jira Administrator, Confluence Administrator, or Jira Service Management Administrator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in Jira Query Language (JQL), advanced reporting, and designing schemes for large user bases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of Agile, Scrum, Kanban, and Waterfall frameworks and how Atlassian tools support them at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with scripting languages (e.g. Groovy, Python) for custom automations is a strong plus.&lt;/li&gt;
